            <h2><span>Bag Balm</span>Works Wonders</h2>
            <p>Vermont’s original Bag Balm provides relief for dry, cracked skin, hands, lips, knees, feet – you name it!</p>

            <p>Since 1899, Bag Balm has been intensely moisturizing and helping protect skin with four simple ingredients – even in the toughest conditions. Bag Balm works wonders for the whole family – for dry paws, it’s a dog’s best friend.</p>

            <p>A small amount of Bag Balm applied to your lips, face, hands, cuticles, feet, elbows, knees or anywhere inbetween works hard to moisturize and soften your severely dry skin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid__item large--seven-twelfths medium--seven-twelfths">
